Package Randomiser

Class GenerateUniqueNumber

java.lang.Object
Randomiser.GenerateUniqueNumber
public class GenerateUniqueNumber extends Object
The GenerateUniqueNumber class generates a unique numeric sequence of a specified length. It provides methods to retrieve the generated number in various data types such as int, long, double, char[] array, and String.

Example usage: 

 GenerateUniqueNumber generator = new GenerateUniqueNumber(5);
 int uniqueInt = generator.toInteger();
